{"tid":1459184,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］［戰術］各位手足求下你地入黎望一望","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:43.000Z","uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b79d1ddc11baa153ba45fc880a5127b225ec3109","tid":1459184,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"原來Be Water有係孫子兵法出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「孫子曰：夫兵形象水，水之形，避高而趨下，兵之形，避實而擊虛。水因地而制流，兵因敵而制勝。故兵無常勢，水無常形。能因敵變化而取勝者，謂之神。」<br />\n個人理解，解錯勿屌<br />\n行兵流如水，避開重防之地，攻其不備之地。<br />\n水無常形，應該無時無刻因應情勢改變策略。<br />\n<br />\n套用返係香港既情況<br />\n即係叫你打遊擊，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有重兵就一定要退，就算要攻都要攻啲不設防佢估唔到既政府建築或者國企</span></strong><br />\n因為流水無形，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>唔應該持續用同一種手法去進攻，要不段變化，唔好俾佢習慣點對付你</strong></span><br />\n應對返啲狗改變圍捕既策略<br />\n<br />\n心態好重要<br />\n琴晚真係好撚嬲加上訓唔到，今朝睇既野變得好唔清晰<br />\n發生咁多事嬲係好正常，但如果上前線一定要平靜啲，唔好有勇無謀<br />\n心躁則暗，心靜則明，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好俾憤怒影響你既判斷</span></strong><br />\n更加重要既係唔好亂，有人數優勢一定要救手足<br />\n每個人都應該要有一個心態<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">「救返個手足代表下次我俾人捉到會多一個手足返黎救我」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n前線組隊提防內鬼<br />\n各自搵識左好耐100%唔係鬼既戰友組左隊先<br />\n其實係現場都有個方法可以判斷係鬼定人<br />\n我唔講咁明<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>「有時歷史係改變唔到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</strong></span><br />\n雖然呢個方法唔係100%<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「但係時間會證明一切」</span></strong><br />\n己所不欲，勿施於人，友善地自己做先，提防啲鬼有位入<br />\n明既手足自己係前線搵多啲同路人<br />\n到時就可以有自己一套既暗號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4e125f02cd6fe25e0bbe2f46be7998841db0d1","tid":1459184,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"3dfb052388c5a456551f68e89140a97ee87dc11b","tid":1459184,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463198a7a0201f35fbca62a0104b136d5f21a05d","tid":1459184,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577bdf81d418dce155e5a477c22bd4ba8a38382c","tid":1459184,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0e979a15cebd48fed4969390c9e206af4b09cd","tid":1459184,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e7b46023bf3967a0b152cd3517f83e71d614d4","tid":1459184,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f588637708521d9d468287408d72c63fd70b3c2e","tid":1459184,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}